{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c6cc337c8","title":"给刘少奇的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"273ffd0382","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":22,"articleId":"4c6cc337c8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5754d593e8","type":"paragraph","text":"给刘少奇的信！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"},{"id":"253c864f8b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月22日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"},{"id":"dea50f73f5","type":"paragraph","text":"北方统一战线非常要紧，特别着重于军队方面，加紧二十九军工作之外，普绥应放在第一位。民族革命同盟则如有些力量，须好好联络，首先推动他们赞助普缓与我们的关系","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"},{"id":"120dd18de9","type":"paragraph","text":"三个方面军已全部在西兰大道会合，内部已基本上统一团结玉阶、特立任前线指挥，在中央与军委决定之下行动。二、四方面军均保存了基本力量并比前进步，一方面军亦加强了。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"},{"id":"8d40ccf83f","type":"paragraph","text":"T11这是毛泽东致刘少奇信的主要内容。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"},{"id":"6a8254d92b","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]民族革命同盟，即中华民族革命同盟，由李济深、陈铭板、蔡廷错等于1935年7月在香港建立的抗日反蒋团体，以“争取民族独立，树立人民政权”为基本政治主张。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"},{"id":"0c244ff08b","type":"paragraph","text":"13]玉阶、特立，指朱德、张国森。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8"}],"page":{"id":"9ebc34286b","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4c6cc337c8","start":250,"end":250}}}},"__N_SSG":true}